casebody.data:
MANASQUAN SAVINGS BANK, Plaintiff,
v.
Lynn SMITH, et al., Defendants-Movants. M-1307 September Term 2017
079551 Supreme Court of New Jersey. June 15, 2018

ORDER

It is ORDERED that the motion for reconsideration of the Court's order dismissing the notice of petition for certification is denied.

JUSTICES ALBIN, PATTERSON, FERNANDEZ-VINA, SOLOMON, and TIMPONE join in this order. CHIEF JUSTICE RABNER did not participate.
